results.deck: Impressions Games specialised in making strategy and management simulation games.
results.description: The company was founded by David Lester in 1989. The company was sold to Sierra Entertainment in 1995, and later become part of Vivendi Universal. The studio was shut down in April 2004, with many studio members forming Tilted Mill Entertainment.
